OL,3,CHead of Nottinghamshire NHS trust
OL,4,Cwhich treated Calocane to retire next
OL,5,Csummer
OL,7,FThe head of Nottinghamshire's mental
OL,8,Fhealth services is to retire after
OL,9,Ffacing criticism about the Nottingham
OL,10,Fattacks inquiry which is set to begin
OL,11,Fnext year.
OL,13,FIfti Majid, the Chief Executive of
OL,14,FNottinghamshire healthcare NHS Trust,
OL,15,Fwill be in post for the public inquiry
OL,16,Fnext year and will retire in June 2026.
