OL,7,FThe Trust treated the killer
OL,8,Fresponsible for the Nottingham
OL,9,Fattacks, Valdo Calocane, who fatally
OL,10,Fstabbed Barnaby Webber, Grace O'Malley
OL,11,FKumar and Ian Coates on June 2023.
OL,13,FThe Trust has faced significant
OL,14,Fscrutiny since the Nottingham attacks.
OL,16,FLast year, a report by the Care
OL,17,FQuality Commission (CQC) found risk
OL,18,Fassessments played down the fact he
OL,19,Fwas refusing to take his medication,
OL,20,Fand was having ongoing and persistent
OL,21,Fsymptoms of psychosis.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
