OL,7,FIt also questions how well the Trust
OL,8,Fengaged with Calocane's family, who
OL,9,Fraised concerns about his mental state.
OL,11,FThe Chief Executive originally
OL,12,Fannounced his plans to retire in
OL,13,FOctober, and has served 42 years in
OL,14,Fthe NHS.
OL,16,FMajid has been in charge of the
OL,17,Fhealthcare provider since December
OL,18,F2022.
