OL,7,FThe judge-led statutory inquiry will
OL,8,Fexamine, among other things, the
OL,9,FTrust's role in caring for Valdo
OL,10,FCalocane who was under their care from
OL,11,FMay 2020 to September 2022.
OL,13,FThe victims' families said the report
OL,14,Fdemonstrated "gross systemic failures
OL,15,Fin the mental health trust."
OL,17,FThe Trust has already been slammed by
OL,18,Fthe victims' families and its
OL,19,Fregulators over failings that led to
OL,20,FCalocane killing three people.
