OL,7,FIn a statement Ifti Majid said:
OL,8,F"Barely a day goes by in this NHS
OL,9,FTrust without me hearing of some
OL,10,Finnovation, act of compassion or extra
OL,11,Feffort that has made a real difference
OL,12,Fto somebody's life.
OL,14,F"That is what gives me hope for the
OL,15,Ffuture of our services and our trust.
OL,16,FThe efforts of our staff and
OL,17,Fvolunteers, on behalf of our patients
OL,18,Fand service users, are truly
OL,19,Fmagnificent.
