OL,7,F"It has been a privilege to work with
OL,8,Fthem, and I am in awe of their
OL,9,Fdedication and passion, often in very
OL,10,Ftough circumstances".
OL,12,FNottinghamshire Healthcare's chair
OL,13,FPaul Devlin said: "I want to thank
OL,14,FIfti for his long career in the
OL,15,Fprovision of mental health, learning
OL,16,Fdisability and autism services.
