OL,7,F"In every role he has held, including
OL,8,Fmost recently as chief executive of
OL,9,Ftwo trusts, he has been driven by a
OL,10,Ffocus on delivering the very best for
OL,11,Fpeople in need.
OL,13,F"His compassion continues to be
OL,14,Finspiring every single day and is a
OL,15,Fwelcome 'north star' in our highly
OL,16,Fpressured NHS".
