OL,7,FTom Cahill CBE, who will become the
OL,8,Ftrust's chair in January, said Mr
OL,9,FMajid's decision to stay on for
OL,10,Fadditional time would enable a "smooth
OL,11,Ftransition".
OL,13,FMr Majid was previously the chief
OL,14,Fexecutive of Derbyshire Healthcare NHS
OL,15,FFoundation Trust.
